Passengers visiting the Royal Jordanian Moscow Office can access a wide range of travel services designed to make trip planning easier and more convenient. The office assists with flight ticket bookings, travel date changes, cancellations, refund requests, and fare upgrade options. Travelers can also receive help with baggage services, including free baggage limits, extra baggage fees, oversized luggage rules, and reporting delayed baggage. The staff provides support for online check-in issues, seat upgrades, boarding pass corrections, and terminal guidance before departure. Families traveling with infants, elderly passengers, and those requiring wheelchair assistance can arrange special support services in advance. Frequent flyers may also inquire about Royal Club membership benefits, reward mileage usage, and class upgrades. By offering clear information and professional assistance, the office helps passengers prepare for their journey smoothly and confidently.

